thread.title_full: Frame My TV reviewed by Ozzy Kim - Interior Designer - OzzyKDesigns LLC

author: Ozzy Kim - Interior Designer - OzzyKDesigns LLC
title: Ozzy Kim - Interior Designer - OzzyKDesigns LLC
text: The precise specifications from Frame My TV assisted in coordinating the technical aspects of the featured installation. At the same time, the extensive frame finish selections, clarity(tv on), refectiveness (tv off), ease of installation, and price point helped to elevate the desired end result within budget. The experience of customer service and quality of product has been outstanding. My clients and myself could not be happier and would highly recommend Frame My TV.
